channel.title: Comments on: Equipment Review: Glass Go Stones (Size 36)

item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: I personally prefer yunzi over glass due to the fact that I like the grainy texture that comes with the stones. In addition, the Black yunzi stones also have a cool green color that you see when you hold it up to the light. xD
